				<cite class="fn">Joe S. </cite><a href="https://krebsonsecurity.com/2021/03/whistleblower-ubiquiti-breach-catastrophic/comment-page-2/#comment-530927"><time datetime="2021-03-31T10:41:20-04:00">March 31, 2021</time></a>			</header><!-- .comment-meta -->

			
			<section class="comment-content comment">
				<p>I wonder how their Amplifi product line is affected by this.  You can use different methods including your Facebook login to manage your AP remotely.  I ended up removing this ability and resetting my Facebook password just in case.  I also disabled the remote VPN (Teleport) as well.</p>
